OL,3,CMan jailed after police link drug
OL,4,Cdealing phone used for restaurant
OL,5,Cbooking
OL,7,FA drug dealer from Tonbridge has been
OL,8,Fconvicted after police linked him to a
OL,9,Fburner phone he used to make a
OL,10,Frestaurant booking.
OL,12,FPolice traced Simon Thorpe and
OL,13,Fsubsequently spotted him on CCTV after
OL,14,Fhe visited a steakhouse in Sevenoaks.
OL,16,FIn February, officers arrested him in
OL,17,FThomas Road in Aylesford, on suspicion
OL,18,Fof supplying cocaine and cannabis, as
OL,19,Fpart of a network known as 'Dave'.
