OL,7,FPolice searched Thorpe's home and
OL,8,Ffound cannabis, with an estimated
OL,9,Fstreet value of #3,000 to #4,000, and
OL,10,Fa phone.
OL,12,FThe phone revealed he had used the
OL,13,Fdevice for personal reasons, such as
OL,14,Ftaking family photos, as well as
OL,15,Fsending marketing messages to over 300
OL,16,Fdrug users in the west Kent area.
