OL,5,Cbooking
OL,7,FThe 34-year-old was charged with being
OL,8,Fconcerned in the supply of cocaine,
OL,9,Fbeing concerned in the supply of
OL,10,Fcannabis, and possession with intent
OL,11,Fto supply cannabis.
OL,13,FThorpe, of Eccles Close, Aylesford,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty before Medway
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on 3 February.
OL,17,FHe was remanded in custody before
OL,18,Fbeing sentenced to three years and two
OL,19,Fmonths in prison on 5 August at
OL,20,FMaidstone Crown Court.
