OL,3,CMan jailed after police link drug
OL,4,Cdealing phone used for restaurant
OL,5,Cbooking
OL,7,FInvestigating officer, PC James
OL,8,FO'Gorman, said: "Throughout the
OL,9,Finvestigation, the offender
OL,10,Fdemonstrated little remorse for the
OL,11,Fimpact of his actions on the local
OL,12,Fcommunity and the lives of the
OL,13,Fvulnerable substance users he took
OL,14,Fadvantage of.
OL,16,F"Thorpe acted in consideration only of
OL,17,Fhis own financial gain but crime does
OL,18,Fnot pay. He will spend the next few
OL,19,Fyears behind bars instead of enjoying
OL,20,Fhis ill-gotten earnings."
